707
00:27:49.270 --> 00:27:50.630
y los rizos

708
00:27:50.710 --> 00:27:52.230
sobre las mejillas.

709
00:27:53.990 --> 00:27:55.190
Como nebo

710
00:27:55.190 --> 00:27:57.590
la retuvo contra la pared,

711
00:27:58.070 --> 00:27:58.790
ella,

712
00:27:59.270 --> 00:28:00.950
riendo y cortada,

713
00:28:01.510 --> 00:28:02.950
