714
00:28:04.335 --> 00:28:05.534
Y el muchacho,

715
00:28:06.175 --> 00:28:07.054
a su frente,

716
00:28:07.775 --> 00:28:09.375
tocándola casi,

717
00:28:10.175 --> 00:28:12.654
